#

Lentil and Mushroom Shepherd's Pie with Cauliflower Mash

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodHeartyVegetarian

Description

A comforting vegetarian twist on the classic shepherd's pie, featuring hearty lentils and mushrooms topped with smooth cauliflower mash.

Ingredients

  • Green Lentils: 1 cup
  • Mushrooms: 2 cups, chopped
  • Carrots: 1 cup, diced
  • Celery: 1 cup, diced
  • Onion: 1, chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Vegetable Broth: 2 cups
  • Tomato Paste: 2 tablespoons
  • Soy Sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • Cauliflower: 1 large head
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Thyme: 1 teaspoon, dried
  • Rosemary: 1 teaspoon, dried
  • Nutmeg: a pinch
